name: Custom Gifts
description:
There are a lot of options for your custom gift!  The image shows just one of the many possibilities.  All combinations are coordinated with complementary fabric.

Choose a custom gift that fits your budget and makes the recipient feel extra special!

name: Christmas Stocking Applique Shirt
description:
I am so excited to be offering this super adorable stocking appliqué shirt just in time for Christmas get-togethers!

A super cute specially-designed stocking appliqué with ultra fuzzy felt cuff is personalized with a felt appliqué of your beautiful boy or girl’s name.   I can also add a little girly bow or handsome bow tie to either shirt.

Please specify below which type of shirt you want.  I will email you to find out what size you want for the shirt after ordering.  

GUARANTEED TO ARRIVE BEFORE CHRISTMAS!

name: Christmas Reindeer Applique Towel Bib
description:
Adorable applique of a reindeer on a stylish red or green bib.  Also includes a super cute girly bow or a handsome bow tie for the little boy or girl on your shopping list! 

Towel is 100% cotton and measures 17" tall x 10.5" wide.  They are a generous size to provide plenty of coverage over baby and helps prevent stains on clothes.  

If you want to order a towel bib with a custom applique, please contact me directly with your ideas.

name: BeeBums Cloth Wipes
description:
Stop using flimsy disposable wipes and start using BeeBums Cloth Wipes!  Each wipe features soft cotton flannel on one side and strong yet gentle micro terry on the other side.  They are GUARANTEED to work better than your regular disposable wipes!

Wipes measure approximately 7" x 7".

Each pack comes with 16 cloth wipes and a solution bottle with the "recipe" printed right on the side.  

Please choose boy, girl, or neutral pattern when ordering.

name: Burp Cloths
description:
Burp cloths can be utilitarian or trendy.  OR they can be both.  These beautiful contoured burp cloths are constructed of soft flannel and absorbent terry cloth.  They are ideal for cleaning up everything from the smallest dribble to the worst reflux.  Not only are they great as burp rags, but they are perfect for wiping delicate baby noses.  You will find so many uses you won't want to leave the house without one!

Many colors and themes available.  See my fabric page on snsbabee.com for current selection.  Specify upon checkout if you prefer a specific flannel design and if ordering more than one, if you want all the same design or a mix of complementary designs.

When ordering 1 to 4 cloths, please select same design or multiple designs.  If you order 5 you get a special discount!
